column19: \"details\":\"Saurabh and Keshav have shared expenses outside this group. On November 29
column20: 2022 Saurabh recorded 1 payment with Keshav that settled their TOTAL Splitwise balance. Splitwise automatically broke this 1 payment down into a set of \\\"Settle all balances\\\" transactions
